      "content": "i tried the hotlines. they just give me the same scripts. they dont get that this isnt just a 'bad mood', it's like a physical weight pulling everything down. it feels like the more i try to struggle, the more the universe just pushes back. do you think there's actually a logic to why life is so much pain for most people?",
